                  "revisionId": 2696102,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Sacrifice triggers immediately after the master being downed during solo play, or when the Bleedout timer reaches zero when playing in a squad."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Sacrifice",
                  "pageId": 262547,
                  "revisionId": 2696102,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "To trigger, Sacrifice must be equipped in a higher-priority (more upper left) slot than Assault Mode , otherwise with any enemies nearby Sentinel will continue attacking them, causing Sacrifice to be suppressed and the master dying without an attempt to be revived."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Sacrifice",
                  "pageId": 262547,
                  "revisionId": 2696102,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "More generally, due to the nature of Precept mods, it is best to place Sacrifice in the very upper left slot, so the sentinel will not prioritize using other skills such as Crowd Dispersion or Ghost over reviving the player. For example, if a Shade has been modded to prioritize Ghost first, it cannot use Sacrifice to revive its owner until Ghost ends. Further, if Ghost comes off cooldown while Shade is reviving the player, the revive will be interrupted by Ghost activating."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Sacrifice",
                  "pageId": 262547,
                  "revisionId": 2696102,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Sacrifice does not work during Arbitrations ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Sacrifice",
                  "pageId": 262547,
                  "revisionId": 2696102,
                  "section": "Notes",
